Our apps require will request access to your devices location information in order to enjoy the full functionality. This location information allows our apps to present your location on the map and to display your tracked route when in tracking mode. Our apps also use your deviceâ€™s compass.
Optionally, you can choose to share your location information via text, email, tweet or Facebook via the Share location functionality. You can also share any stored route created via email, iCloud or any other sharing mechanism supported by Apple (e.g. Dropbox).
No data is ever transmitted anywhere else and JOMO Solutions does not collect any information whatsoever about the users of their products.